1
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,640
Wang Jingwei is preparing to set up a puppet government.

2
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:40,520
I'm worried that the situation of the War of Resistance in the future

3
00:01:40,520 --> 00:01:42,450
will become increasingly severe.

4
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:44,880
When we attacked Sanhuang Village occupied by Japanese invaders,

5
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,560
Ge Zhiyuan sent his intelligence agent team

6
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,680
to ambush us.

7
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,039
Fortunately, we had enough people

8
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,039
and were prepared,

9
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:51,360
so they couldn't make a move.

10
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:53,920
Did he collude with the Japanese Puppet Army in advance?

11
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,200
I wouldn't dare say anything without evidence.

12
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,479
But he's been flirting with

13
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,759
the KMT provincial chairman,

14
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:00,960
who was just appointed as

15
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,760
the Brigade Commander of the Third Security Brigade of Jiangsu.

16
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,890
He just wants to expand his territory.

17
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,320
What about Ge Zhiyuan?

18
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:08,280
I don't think he wants to fight the Japanese at all.

19
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,479
He just hides from the Japanese

20
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:11,520
and bullies the commoners with exorbitant taxes.

21
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,760
Chairman Mao once said

22
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,200
for long-term cooperation

23
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,520
within the united front,

24
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,960
mutual help and concession among various parties and groups

25
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,820
are necessary.

26
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,400
But it should be positive,

27
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,360
not negative.

28
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,680
Fortunately, this battle didn't happen.

29
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,320
This way,

30
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,010
we'll go talk to Ge Zhiyuan.

31
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:28,200
Even if we can't reach a peace agreement,

32
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:30,560
it'll buy us time to grow stronger.

33
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:34,940
At worst, it'll prevent him from easily turning to the Japanese Puppet Army.

34
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:35,760
Let's talk inside.

35
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,560
Okay.

36
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,170
District Chief.

37
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,720
No tail.

38
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,170
Brother Ziming.

39
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:02,370
You've worked hard.

40
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,680
I need to confirm something with you.

41
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:07,810
Regarding Tian Jiatai.

42
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,800
Although he contacted us before

43
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,940
and fought against the Japanese,

44
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,360
he only moved his factory inland.

45
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:17,170
That's his only contribution.

46
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:20,840
Now the Japanese are spreading propaganda everywhere,

47
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,920
saying he cooperated with the Japanese

48
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:25,200
and was forced to commit suicide by the Bureau of Investigation and Statistics.

49
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:27,760
We plan to remain silent about this

50
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,800
and only heavily promote

51
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:32,040
your assassination mission in the newspapers.

52
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:34,079
But Tian Jiatai committed suicide.

53
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:37,060
I witnessed his last action with my own eyes.

54
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:41,370
The organization sent you to protect him.

55
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,810
And what was the result?

56
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:43,840
I don't think you want

57
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:46,500
the whole country to laugh at our failed mission

58
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,840
and the loss of Tian Jiatai's life.

59
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,200
We can take this opportunity

60
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:53,240
to deter traitors of all sizes

61
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:55,300
and boost national prestige.

62
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,320
It's said that

63
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:00,000
a cook in Tian Mansion made a false confession.

64
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,640
Let the enemy fabricate lies.

65
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,130
District Chief,

66
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:07,360
that cook is also one of our men.

67
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:10,200
He helped a lot in this mission.

68
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,760
But he has a family to support

69
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:13,160
and couldn't escape in time,

70
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,720
so he was caught and taken to No. 76.

71
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,920
We have to rescue him.

72
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:17,920
Brother Ziming,

73
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:22,010
your current situation is extremely dangerous.

74
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,640
The enemy is searching for you like crazy.

75
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,600
He's just an insignificant nobody.

76
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,840
He'll suffer a little physical pain

77
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,480
and will be released in a few days.

78
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,440
Then we have to rescue his family.

79
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:33,560
We will rescue them,

80
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,040
but not now.

81
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:38,360
There are more urgent tasks for you to do.

82
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,160
Did you sleep well last night?

83
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,160
I've done my part.

84
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,080
Now it's time for you to do yours.

85
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,570
First, you need to confess.

86
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,440
Second, you need to cooperate.

87
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:15,640
Tell me everything you know about the personnel of the Shanghai District,

88
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:17,400
teams, names, addresses,

89
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:19,080
and other working contacts.

90
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,000
Tell me everything.

91
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:26,280
Make sure you write down every single word.

92
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:31,280
We're in this together now.

93
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,010
No need to bluff each other.

94
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:36,720
They say, keep one's mouth shut and guard your thoughts like a fortress.

95
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,850
But you should know,

96
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,260
a bottle can be broken,

97
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:43,360
and no matter how thick the fortress walls are, they can be breached.

98
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,120
If you don't talk,

99
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:53,159
I'll have no choice but to go after the old man

100
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:54,520
and your madam.

101
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:04,010
Captain Ma, how long have you been holding me?

102
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,280
Twelve days.

103
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:06,160
Right.

104
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,680
In Shanghai, the people who know who I am

105
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,320
are only a handful.

106
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:14,320
I've been in trouble for twelve days.

107
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:18,200
Wouldn't the ones who needed to run have already run?

108
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:20,800
I'm telling you, it's useless.

109
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,080
In Shanghai,

110
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:25,000
who is your direct superior?

111
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,930
I don't have a direct superior.

112
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:31,640
Are you saying you report directly to Chongqing?

113
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,820
Who delivers messages to you?

114
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,120
Blindy Huang.

115
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:46,370
Is he in the action team or the intelligence team?

116
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:48,760
Action team.

117
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,659
Then where is your radio station?

118
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:59,520
With Blindy Huang, at Chuan-Shan Noodle House.

119
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:24,160
Director Lin.

120
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,800
Director Lin.

121
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,120
This is a big fish.

122
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:32,400
I haven't finished interrogating. Listen a bit more.

123
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,440
Thank you for conducting the interrogation personally. You've worked hard.

124
00:07:36,440 --> 00:07:37,200
It's my duty.

125
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,080
This man and this sword,

126
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:42,920
are my gifts to you for joining the Secret Service Headquarters.

127
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,680
Let me tell you this.

128
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:51,080
He is not some Major General of the Bureau of Investigation and Statistics,

129
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:52,159
nor is he Tieshu.

130
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,120
He's just a cook.

131
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,440
Deal with it quickly.

132
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:00,200
It was my oversight.

133
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,530
Don't worry, I'll handle it properly.

134
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,080
I'm leaving.

135
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,400
Director Lin.

136
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,280
That sword,

137
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,280
isn't it your gift to me?

138
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:15,880
Please keep it.

139
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,880
Jiangtian.

140
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,080
Welcome to the Secret Service Headquarters,

141
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:29,400
back to the ranks of our fellow Chinese.

142
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,120
It has always been my greatest hope.

143
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,240
Take care, Director.

144
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,850
What are you so arrogant about?

145
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,920
Let go of me!

146
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,360
Traitor!

147
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:53,560
Even if you kill my people,

148
00:08:54,160 --> 00:08:56,880
you can't kill my patriotism.

149
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,400
Kill us all if you dare!

150
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,200
You will die a horrible death!

151
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:09,300
Traitors! You will die a horrible death!

152
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:11,400
Move it! Faster!

153
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:13,240
I have failed my ancestors!

154
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,200
Traitors!

155
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,760
Harm Chinese people!

156
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:21,440
Can you face your ancestors?

157
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,520
Shut up!

158
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:24,200
Kill us if you have the guts.

159
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,120
Move. Keep moving.

160
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,360
You'll die a horrible death.

161
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,360
Hurry up.

162
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:30,720
Traitors.

163
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:31,400
Get in.

164
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,680
Traitors.

165
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:33,960
Hurry up.

166
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,120
Wanfu,

167
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:53,240
which direction is No. 76 in Shanghai?

168
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,800
This is the International Settlement,

169
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:58,920
an extra-settlement road area.

170
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:01,320
It's considered the west side of Shanghai.

171
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,560
Then,

172
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:07,480
Mr. Tian's home is to the east of here.

173
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:10,360
Right.

174
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:14,800
Mr. Tian is a righteous man.

175
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,360
A righteous man.

176
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,520
Let's bow to him.

177
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:44,160
To be imprisoned.

178
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:46,880
It seems for the rest of my life,

179
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:51,680
I, Zhang Ruxian, will be entangled with imprisonment.

180
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:55,880
Alas.

181
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:14,360
I was imprisoned in the north, sitting in a mud room.

182
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:19,160
The room is eight feet wide and four xun deep.

183
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:24,240
The single door is low and small, the white walls are short and narrow.

184
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:28,240
It's dirty and dark down there.

185
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:33,080
Father, what are you muttering?

186
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:37,720
This is Wen Tianxiang's 'The Song of Righteousness'.

187
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,800
Then let me stay in this prison

188
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:45,800
and nurture my noble spirit.

189
00:11:59,040 --> 00:11:59,800
Master,

190
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,690
please teach me to read.

191
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:08,280
Teach me to read.

192
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:14,480
The sun is really rising from the west.

193
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:17,480
Didn't you always hate these things,

194
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:20,820
and hate me talking about things you don't understand?

195
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,760
Why are you making fun of me?

196
00:12:22,880 --> 00:12:25,000
I really want to learn to read from you.

197
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,600
I also sincerely want to understand what you're saying.

198
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:30,160
I've suffered all my life for being uneducated.

199
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:32,560
I'm so sincere, and you're making fun of me.

200
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:37,720
Learning requires perseverance.

201
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:38,960
What?

202
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:40,080
Perseverance.

203
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:41,120
Perseverance.

204
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:46,440
Without perseverance, one will indulge in depravity and extravagance.

205
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,120
Everyone is for themselves.

206
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:48,720
No, Master,

207
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,250
what are you talking about?

208
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:53,320
I really want to learn from you.

209
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,600
What are you doing here,

210
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,800
farting dog, dog farting?

211
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,000
What do you mean?

212
00:12:59,160 --> 00:13:00,040
What?

213
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:04,000
Wanfu, this 'gou' is not that 'dog'.

214
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:07,040
This 'pi' is not that 'fart'.

215
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:10,720
'Gou' means 'if'.

216
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:12,840
'Gou wu heng xin'

217
00:13:13,440 --> 00:13:17,040
means if you don't have perseverance.

218
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:19,840
'Pi' and 'xie' mean improper,

219
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:21,560
improper things.

220
00:13:22,040 --> 00:13:25,160
'Fang pi xie chi' means

221
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:28,560
if you don't have a stable mind,

222
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:32,120
you'll break the law and do all kinds of evil.

223
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:34,560
You can do any bad thing.

224
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:35,840
Perseverance

225
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:38,440
means having the determination to persist

226
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,880
and never give up until the goal is reached.

227
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:44,560
If you give up carving, even rotten wood cannot be broken.

228
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:48,330
If you keep carving, you can cut through metal and stone.

229
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:51,000
Do you understand?

230
00:13:51,920 --> 00:13:53,120
I understand.

231
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,920
I understood this sentence.

232
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:57,320
Master, I sincerely want to learn from you.

233
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,480
When I learn well,

234
00:13:58,840 --> 00:14:00,900
I'll understand everything you say.

235
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:04,600
But Wanfu,

236
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:08,680
there are rules for learning from me.

237
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,240
Alright, tell me.

238
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:14,240
If you can't remember and memorize it,

239
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:17,240
I'll smack your palms and kick your butt.

240
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:20,040
Alright, if I can't remember it,

241
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,760
you can smack my palms

242
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,400
and kick my butt all you want.

243
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:28,370
Let me teach you to memorize something first.

244
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,440
Sure.

245
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:30,480
Come on.

246
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:40,320
This is an essay of a thousand characters,

247
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:43,920
but not a single character is repeated.

248
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:47,240
If you can recognize all of them

249
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:49,560
and remember them,

250
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:52,760
you can not only read books and newspapers

251
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:56,200
but even write your own essays.

252
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:58,160
Is there really such a good deal?

253
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:59,760
I-I-I'll learn. I'll learn.

254
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:03,680
Alright, let's begin.

255
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:09,690
The sky was black and the earth was yellow, the universe was vast and desolate.

256
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:13,880
The sky was black and the earth was yellow,

257
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:16,320
the u-u-universe was vast and desolate.

258
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:20,280
The sun waxes and wanes, and the stars are arrayed in the sky.

259
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:25,160
The sun waxes and wanes, and the stars are arrayed in the sky.

260
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:30,160
As seasons change, we reap in autumn and store in winter.

261
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:34,960
As seasons change, we reap in autumn and store in winter.

262
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,730
Aren't you trying Tian Jiatai's case?

263
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,160
Is it over so soon?

264
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:43,400
Whose is it?

265
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,240
Tell me,

266
00:15:45,560 --> 00:15:47,420
could this thing belong to a cook?

267
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:49,730
You're kidding.

268
00:15:50,280 --> 00:15:52,240
What kind of cook would have this?

269
00:15:53,680 --> 00:15:54,940
That's why I'm saying,

270
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,860
Ma Jiangtian is as stupid as a pig.

271
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,200
A cook,

272
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:01,460
yet he insists on guessing he's some Tieshu.

273
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:03,450
Even if it's not Tieshu,

274
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:06,200
it could really be a General.

275
00:16:14,280 --> 00:16:15,120
But,

276
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:17,120
if Tian Mansion really

277
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:19,040
hid a General,

278
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:23,560
Tian Jiatai wouldn't have been forced to death.

279
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,820
He would've run away long ago.

280
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:27,440
You...

281
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:31,600
you're just resenting him for not sponsoring you back then.

282
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,200
Right?

283
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:35,000
Stop it.

284
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:37,360
Am I wrong?

285
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,120
Yes.

286
00:16:39,520 --> 00:16:40,580
But let me tell you,

287
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:44,120
Ma Jiangtian also played a trick.

288
00:16:44,800 --> 00:16:45,520
He

289
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:48,320
released the cook's wife.

290
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:50,840
Said he wants to play the long game.

291
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,600
Even though he's stupid,

292
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,440
he is quite diligent.

293
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:57,370
Being diligent is good.

294
00:16:57,720 --> 00:17:00,800
But it has to be used in the right place, right?

295
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,800
It hurts holding this thing.

296
00:17:04,040 --> 00:17:06,119
I don't even use it for killing chickens or fish.

297
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:08,050
Don't keep it at home. It's creepy.

298
00:17:08,760 --> 00:17:10,240
Throw it away immediately.

299
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,079
Got it.

300
00:17:29,560 --> 00:17:30,280
Mrs. Fu,

301
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,210
you are here so early today.

302
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:33,960
Yes.

303
00:17:34,120 --> 00:17:34,800
Okay, wait here.

304
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:36,280
I have two more dirty clothes.

305
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:36,840
Okay.

306
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:39,120
Okay, thank you.

307
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:40,480
Okay, I'll wash them and bring them to you.

308
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:41,200
Okay.

309
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:55,760
The sky was black and the earth was yellow, the universe was vast and desolate.

310
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:59,090
The sun waxes and wanes, and the stars are arrayed in the sky.

311
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:03,760
As seasons change, we reap in autumn and store in winter.

312
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:08,240
Extra days form a leap year, and the musical pipes regulate the seasons.

313
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:11,360
Rising clouds make rain, and dew congeals into frost.

314
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:15,480
Gold is born in the Lishui River, and jade comes from the Kunlun Mountains.

315
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:19,480
The sword is called Juque, and the pearl is called Ye Guang.

316
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:20,920
Right?

317
00:19:24,160 --> 00:19:24,880
Auntie.

318
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:27,220
Someone told me to give you a note.

319
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:28,120
Who?

320
00:19:28,440 --> 00:19:29,440
I don't know them.

321
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:43,600
Sis, stop talking about me.

322
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:46,050
Where have you been this past year?

323
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:53,800
Let me show you something first.

324
00:20:10,080 --> 00:20:13,680
A receipt for donating cotton uniforms to the New Fourth Army.

325
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:14,680
Yes.

326
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:16,360
It's just a pity

327
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:19,560
that Mr. Tian is no longer with us.

328
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:26,960
This past year,

329
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,640
I've been to many places.

330
00:20:29,360 --> 00:20:30,120
I went to

331
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:33,440
the Army Headquarters of the New Fourth Army in Southern Anhui.

332
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,640
I also went to Wuxi

333
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:37,200
and the guerrilla forces in Jiangyin.

334
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,320
I saw a

335
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,560
brand-new, ideal,

336
00:20:40,960 --> 00:20:42,760
and hopeful world.

337
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:46,360
Do you know about the Jiangsu Anti-Japanese Army's night raid on Xushuguan

338
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:48,000
and the battle at Hongqiao Airport?

339
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:48,720
I know.

340
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:51,320
They blew up four Japanese Army planes.

341
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:53,520
Those few days, everyone was talking about it,

342
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,600
asking if the New Fourth Army was

343
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:55,960
going to attack Shanghai.

344
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:58,160
Their strength is not enough right now,

345
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:01,040
but they are growing very rapidly.

346
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,840
Coming back to Shanghai this time

347
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:04,120
is to continue

348
00:21:04,120 --> 00:21:05,850
providing them with supplies.

349
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:08,400
Did you join them?

350
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:14,720
Xuefei.

351
00:21:15,600 --> 00:21:16,520
I cooked some noodles for you.

352
00:21:16,520 --> 00:21:17,280
Come, clear this space.

353
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:17,800
Okay.

354
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:20,800
Come.

355
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:24,120
Eat some noodles.

356
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:27,360
Can you help keep an eye on the outside?

357
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:28,420
Okay, don't worry.

358
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:34,080
Right now,

359
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:36,930
intelligence agents are too rampant.

360
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:40,360
There are those from the Jiang family, the Wang family,

361
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:41,600
and the Japanese.

362
00:21:41,760 --> 00:21:42,640
So from now on,

363
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:45,320
my work will be more hidden.

364
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:47,660
I won't appear in public anymore.

365
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,200
Sis.

366
00:22:04,360 --> 00:22:05,280
I can help you.

367
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:08,440
For occasions where it's inconvenient for you to show up,

368
00:22:08,440 --> 00:22:09,640
you can leave it to me.

369
00:22:10,280 --> 00:22:11,720
I know it's dangerous,

370
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:14,200
but from the bottom of my heart,

371
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,600
I hope to do something for you

372
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:19,730
and for the war of resistance within my power.

373
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:23,130
Every time I think of the fundraising period,

374
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,680
I feel a wave of heat

375
00:22:24,760 --> 00:22:26,080
surging in my heart.

376
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:28,970
Ever since Yunkui left,

377
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,810
I feel that only this matter

378
00:22:32,080 --> 00:22:34,040
makes me feel alive.

379
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:37,370
I want to live a more valuable life.

380
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:42,440
Yujiao, well said.

381
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:44,240
Welcome.

382
00:22:47,920 --> 00:22:48,680
Do you know?

383
00:22:49,080 --> 00:22:50,140
My return this time

384
00:22:50,320 --> 00:22:52,320
was exactly to see you for this.

385
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:55,880
I remember you told me

386
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:58,460
that you studied accounting before, right?

387
00:22:58,480 --> 00:23:00,340
My maiden family runs a silk shop.

388
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:01,760
When it was busy before,

389
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:03,200
I would help the Manager

390
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,260
with the accounts.

391
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,520
That will do.

392
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:08,240
We happen to have a trading company.

393
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:10,880
You should go back and pack up quickly,

394
00:23:11,320 --> 00:23:13,180
and move here as soon as possible.

395
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:17,180
As for the situations you just mentioned...

396
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:19,680
They mistook Wanfu for Zhang Yunkui.

397
00:23:20,120 --> 00:23:22,580
I think it's actually a double-edged sword.

398
00:23:23,600 --> 00:23:24,920
First of all, as for us,

399
00:23:25,360 --> 00:23:26,620
we cannot give up hope.

400
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:28,720
We should go visit them often

401
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:30,920
in the name of their family to deliver clothes.

402
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:33,840
This will help us gather intelligence.

403
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:37,120
Okay.

404
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:38,840
Try this.

405
00:23:38,840 --> 00:23:40,960
See how Dr. Chen's cooking is.

406
00:23:43,600 --> 00:23:44,320
Careful.

407
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:51,440
Excuse me, coming through.

408
00:23:57,320 --> 00:23:58,250
It's right here.

409
00:23:58,960 --> 00:24:00,080
Jiyun Trading Company.

410
00:24:00,080 --> 00:24:01,680
We are here, Yueming.

411
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:02,340
We're here.

412
00:24:02,480 --> 00:24:03,160
Take care, Mr. Zhang.

413
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:03,800
Okay.

414
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,040
Yueming, we're here.

415
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:06,760
Ms. Liu.

416
00:24:07,560 --> 00:24:08,240
Han.

417
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:09,280
Welcome back, Ms. Liu.

418
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:10,960
Come, let me introduce you.

419
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:12,160
Jinsheng,

420
00:24:12,520 --> 00:24:13,520
this is Mrs. Ding,

421
00:24:13,840 --> 00:24:14,800
and this is Yueming.

422
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:15,360
Hello.

423
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:16,680
Hello.

424
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:17,560
Call him Uncle.

425
00:24:17,560 --> 00:24:18,080
Uncle.

426
00:24:18,560 --> 00:24:19,160
Yueming.

427
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:20,360
Let's go inside to talk.

428
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:21,620
Okay, let's settle in.

429
00:24:21,800 --> 00:24:22,640
Come, let me take that.

430
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:23,680
Thank you.

431
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:24,640
Slow down.

432
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:27,440
You're so good, Yueming.

433
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:28,160
Here, Mrs. Ding.

434
00:24:28,160 --> 00:24:30,080
Thank you, Yueming.

435
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:36,520
Yujiao, the conditions here are a bit tough.

436
00:24:36,760 --> 00:24:39,020
It's going to be hard on you and the child.

437
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:40,280
Not at all, Ms. Zeng.

438
00:24:40,360 --> 00:24:41,400
It's very nice here.

439
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:43,880
Comfortable, neat, and clean.

440
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:46,840
Ms. Liu.

441
00:24:50,040 --> 00:24:50,800
Yueming,

442
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:52,280
we'll live here from now on, okay?

443
00:24:52,280 --> 00:24:52,760
Okay.

444
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:53,520
All right.

445
00:24:54,280 --> 00:24:56,560
Han, take the kid out to play.

446
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,040
Sure.

447
00:24:58,120 --> 00:25:00,380
Yueming, Uncle will take you out to play.

448
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,160
Come.

449
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:03,000
Your shoes.

450
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:03,680
Your shoe fell off.

451
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,840
Come, let Uncle help you.

452
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:05,960
It fell off again.

453
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:07,600
Uncle will put it back on for you.

454
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:08,120
Later,

455
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:09,760
I will take you

456
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:11,880
to see the orphanage.

457
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,000
Once we are there,

458
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:15,330
we can't make any mistakes with names.

459
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:16,680
Okay.

460
00:25:21,640 --> 00:25:22,320
Sis,

461
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:25,770
how did you become a teacher at the orphanage?

462
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:28,520
It's all because of Dr. Chen.

463
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:29,960
He is

464
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:34,360
a director of the Cihong Charity Hall.

465
00:25:34,560 --> 00:25:35,560
After I came back,

466
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,520
I needed a new identity.

467
00:25:37,640 --> 00:25:38,640
Coincidentally,

468
00:25:38,760 --> 00:25:41,490
the affiliated orphanage was short of teachers,

469
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:44,280
so they placed me there.

470
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:45,730
Because of this,

471
00:25:46,640 --> 00:25:48,840
our Jiyun Trading Company

472
00:25:49,240 --> 00:25:51,680
was opened right next to the orphanage.

473
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:53,000
Okay.

474
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:56,920
When you're busy during the day,

475
00:25:58,200 --> 00:25:59,730
just leave Yueming with me.

476
00:26:00,600 --> 00:26:01,320
Great.

477
00:26:01,600 --> 00:26:03,240
If I have free time,

478
00:26:03,320 --> 00:26:05,320
I'll go to the Orphanage to help out.

479
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:06,800
Yujiao,

480
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:07,800
sit down.

481
00:26:11,840 --> 00:26:12,520
Yujiao.

482
00:26:13,280 --> 00:26:15,800
Although the storefront is small,

483
00:26:17,120 --> 00:26:19,920
it's an important liaison point for the New Fourth Army in Shanghai

484
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:21,160
along the

485
00:26:21,160 --> 00:26:22,440
supply line.

486
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:27,320
From now on, your responsibilities will be heavy.

487
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:31,690
Procuring daily necessities is relatively simple.

488
00:26:31,720 --> 00:26:34,240
But when it comes to military supplies

489
00:26:34,320 --> 00:26:35,880
controlled by the Japanese Army,

490
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:37,740
it becomes extremely difficult.

491
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:41,010
You could say the biggest challenge is transportation.

492
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:42,680
You should know that

493
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,600
from the concession to the base,

494
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,600
there are countless checkpoints.

495
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,160
Of course,

496
00:26:49,560 --> 00:26:50,280
you

497
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:52,080
don't need to worry too much.

498
00:26:54,120 --> 00:26:54,960
You should

499
00:26:55,080 --> 00:26:57,960
slowly get familiar with the work here.

500
00:26:58,800 --> 00:27:00,600
I will gradually

501
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:03,280
introduce the work to you.

502
00:27:04,080 --> 00:27:04,840
Okay.

503
00:27:05,320 --> 00:27:06,120
Keep it up.

504
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:13,680
Master.

505
00:27:15,720 --> 00:27:17,320
This Qu Yuan you told me about

506
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,000
is so interesting.

507
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:23,280
He comes from a good family, is good-looking, kind-hearted,

508
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,060
and affectionate.

509
00:27:27,720 --> 00:27:29,850
He cut water chestnut leaves into a top

510
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,680
and wove lotus flowers into a skirt.

511
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,600
His hat was so high,

512
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:34,000
and his sword was so long.

513
00:27:34,560 --> 00:27:35,760
He is so interesting.

514
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:38,760
Then what exactly do you like about him?

515
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:44,840
Well, of course I like him for

516
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:47,970
'I heave a long sigh and wipe away my tears;

517
00:27:48,520 --> 00:27:50,560
I grieve for the hardship of my people's lives.'

518
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:52,360
'It is what my heart holds dear;

519
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:55,840
for it I'd have no regrets even if I'd have to die a thousand times.'

520
00:27:55,840 --> 00:27:56,320
But Master,

521
00:27:56,320 --> 00:27:57,580
I still want to ask you,

522
00:27:57,600 --> 00:27:58,720
his sis already told him

523
00:27:58,720 --> 00:28:00,520
that everyone likes to form cliques

524
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:02,080
and act opportunistically.

525
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:04,560
Why didn't Qu Yuan listen?

526
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:08,200
Why did he insist on looking for Emperor Shun?

527
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:10,280
Did he find him in the end?

528
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:13,440
This is just the beginning.

529
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:18,760
We'll continue the search today.

530
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:26,520
'I bade the sun-god to stay his course;

531
00:28:28,040 --> 00:28:31,720
Gazing at Yanzi Mountain, wishing time would not press on.'

532
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:36,200
'The road ahead is long and arduous;

533
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:39,800
I shall seek high and low in my quest.'

534
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:42,760
What does that mean?

535
00:28:42,760 --> 00:28:46,760
Life is short, seize the day.

536
00:28:47,520 --> 00:28:48,320
Wanfu.

537
00:28:49,000 --> 00:28:50,960
Look at the moonlight,

538
00:28:51,520 --> 00:28:53,640
and you will see yourself.

539
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,840
Avalokiteshvara.

540
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:01,240
The road is long,

541
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:04,440
is still long and arduous,

542
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:08,920
I shall seek high and low in my quest.

543
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:25,080
Planting the green seedlings all over the field,

544
00:29:26,320 --> 00:29:29,280
lower your head and you will see the sky in the water.

545
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:34,120
All six sense organs are pure, and only then one comprehends,

546
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:35,560
to retreat is

547
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:38,200
to advance.

548
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:41,160
To retreat is to advance.

549
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,560
It's about planting rice seedlings.

550
00:29:42,560 --> 00:29:43,360
Right.

551
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:46,280
Makes sense.

552
00:29:47,320 --> 00:29:49,120
Actually, this same piece of land

553
00:29:49,120 --> 00:29:51,320
looks different in different weather.

554
00:29:51,320 --> 00:29:52,920
It has a different feel to it.

555
00:29:53,640 --> 00:29:54,770
The color of the soil

556
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:57,200
and the color of these seedlings

557
00:29:57,240 --> 00:29:58,520
are completely different.

558
00:29:58,520 --> 00:30:00,650
The more you look, the more you like it.

559
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:02,160
Crops can't move.

560
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:03,560
What's so interesting about them?

561
00:30:03,560 --> 00:30:05,160
I like looking at livestock.

562
