During the Battle of Xikou Town last year,

843
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:22,240
I doubted the identity of Zhang Dougui.

844
00:42:22,840 --> 00:42:26,320
Later, I had a private chat with Magistrate Fan

845
00:42:26,640 --> 00:42:29,320
and finally confirmed your identity.

846
00:42:32,400 --> 00:42:34,360
Mr. Dai asked me to keep it a secret

847
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:37,970
and come to reward you in the name of Commander Gu.

848
00:42:38,120 --> 00:42:39,800
When Mr. Dai has the chance,

849
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:42,400
he will report to the Generalissimo

850
00:42:42,640 --> 00:42:44,440
to restore your party membership

851
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:45,800
and restore your reputation.

852
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,840
He specifically said,

853
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:48,800
especially now behind enemy lines,

854
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,160
it's the time to use people.

855
00:42:50,160 --> 00:42:52,820
Your rank and position should both be promoted.

856
00:42:52,960 --> 00:42:53,840
General Zhang,

857
00:42:54,080 --> 00:42:56,920
my congratulations.

858
00:42:57,400 --> 00:42:58,460
Congratulations.

859
00:42:59,880 --> 00:43:00,920
Thank the Party-State for its cultivation.

860
00:43:00,920 --> 00:43:01,920
Thank you, Mr. Dai.

861
00:43:01,920 --> 00:43:03,780
Officer Pan has a discerning eye.

862
00:43:03,800 --> 00:43:04,720
Let's sit down and talk.
